            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2200.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is cooking, tear your<strong> ciabatta[s]</strong> into bite-sized pieces and add to a baking tray (or two!) with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong> and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong></p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 6-7 min or until crisp and golden – these are your<strong> ciabatta croutons</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
